<a data-tip="p$t$wang-tian-qi-49" href="/people/wang-tian-qi-49">王天祺</a>，<strong title="南七技校技工，物理逃兵" class="zu-question-my-bio">南七技校技工，物理逃兵</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
