<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="86">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zif-97" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zif-97" class="zg-link" title="Zif">Zif</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$a-bu-si-79" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/a-bu-si-79" class="zg-link" title="一把小灰狗">一把小灰狗</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
